name: priority seat
description:
From the Hong Kong 2016 series. Perfectly framed the advertising video screen behind the MTR Train to show in the window (this was random luck). Even luckier was the advert appears to be promoting first class seating in an airline. On a crowded train, all seats are luxury to those in need of it.

First of what will be many pieces exploring the useless, decayed, discarded, ignored, redundant, empty  and under-utilised. 

Original image, no video or sound. No prints have or will be sold. I retain all copyright. 

4000x2667
